.. you'll be signed up for the same basic package of channels, dubbed Ultimate TV. This bundle includes a Netflix subscription and shows from US streaming service Peacock.</p><p>Crucially, this isn't a Netflix subscription that&nbsp;<em>only&nbsp;</em>works on your Sky box &ndash; it's a fully-fledged subscription that you can watch on&nbsp;<em>any</em> Netflix app, including those on iPhone, iPad, Fire TV, and Android. Viewing history and Watchlist will be synchronised across devices, so you'll see any changes made on your phone reflected on your Sky kit, and vice versa.</p><p>If you already have a Netflix subscription, you'll be able to keep your existing account with viewing history and bundle the monthly bill as part of your Sky subscription so that it's easier to manage. It also means you won't start from scratch with new recommendations based on your tastes.</p></div><div class="p402_hide text-description"><div class="youtube_video"><iframe data-src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/WyBpkPQUhcQ" width="590" height="332"  allowfullscreen data-lazy-function="iframe"></iframe></div></div><div class="text-description"><h2 id="Best-Sky-deals-with-Netflix-60557150" data-toc="1">Best Sky deals with Netflix</h2></div><div class="text-description"><p>Since October 2019, Sky has included a Netflix subscription with <em>all</em> of&nbsp;its TV bundles.</p><p>Currently branded as the <a data-link-tracking="InArticle|Link" href="https://www.awin1.com/cread.php?awinmid=11005&amp;awinaffid=213635&amp;campaign=&amp;clickref=Express---ExpressRated-&amp;ued=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sky.com%2Fglass%2Fbuy%2Fstream%2Ftv-packs&amp;platform=pl" rel="nofollow" onclick="ExpressApp.GoogleAnalytics.TrackEvent('Affiliate NetworkEvent', 'AWIN')"><strong>Sky Entertainment bundle</strong></a>, this entry-level package of channels includes access to some 150 linear channels unavailable on Freeview, 500 on-demand boxsets from Sky Originals and HBO, and that all-important&nbsp;Netflix subscription.</p><