ming on the all-new set-top box from October 19, 2022.</p><p>Sky originally confirmed plans to offer Sky Stream back in April 2022, although the hardware was originally unveiled alongside Sky Glass back in late 2021.</p><p>Sky Stream is shipped to customers with instructions to setup the kit &ndash; but there's no engineer visit or satellite dish installation needed. Instead, it's simply a case of plugging in the Sky Stream puck, plugging in a HDMI cable into your chosen telly, and connecting to Wi-Fi by following the on-screen guide. And that's it.</p></div><div class="photo changeSpace"><p class="withoutCaption"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://cdn.images.express.co.uk/img/dynamic/59/940x/secondary/sky-stream-plugged-into-television-4348667.webp?r=1710321272257" media="screen"><img src="https://cdn.images.express.co.uk/img/dynamic/59/940x/secondary/sky-stream-plugged-into-television-4348667.jpg?r=1710321272257" alt="sky stream plugged into television" title="sky stream plugged into television" width="940" height="558" loading="lazy"></picture></p><span class="newsCaption">Sky Stream has a much smaller footprint than Sky Q <span class="caption">(Image: SKY)</span></span></div><div class="text-description"><p>Sky has confirmed that Sky Stream customers will need a minimum download speed of 10Mbps to watch live channels and stream on-demand boxsets. Of course, those who want to watch in the highest quality available &ndash; the diddy set-top box supports Ultra HD, HDR and Dolby surround sound &ndash; will need more bandwidth than that. It's possible to have up to six Sky Stream boxes running simultaneously in different rooms of the house for a multi-room experience, although this requires faster broadband too.</p><p>For those who live in a home with a clear line-of-sight for a Sky satellite dish or in a block of flats without a communal dish, Sky Stream could be the first time they're able to get access to exclusive live channels from Sky, on-demand boxsets from HBO, Sky Originals, and US streaming service Peacock.</p><p>Sky Stream is available with either an 18-month minimum term contract or a 31-day rolling contract. The latter costs &pound;3 extra each month, but is perfect for those who want to be able to cancel and switch between bundles of channels (Sky Cinema, Sky Sports) at the drop of a hat.</p><p>Speaking about the arrival of Sky Stream, Executive Vice President and CEO for UK and Europe Stephen van Rooyen said: &ldquo;Sky&rsquo;s always reinvented the TV experience and offered the best content &ndash; but it&rsquo;s not always been accessible to everyone. There couldn&rsquo;t be a better time to launch our latest innovation using the Sky Glass Platform &ndash; whether you want to stream House of the Dragon, Gangs of London or Stranger Things, Sky Stream has it all. It&rsquo;s the most affordable and easiest way to get Sky TV and Netflix together, offering consumers the value they are seeking right now.&rdquo;</p></div><div class="partners-element single"><div class="widget blurb" data-expires="" data-alt-exp-text="" data-id="31323" data-name="Get Sky TV + Netflix and broadband"><div class="data"><div class="images"> <a href="https://www.awin1.com/cread.php?awinmid=11005&awinaffid=213635&campaign=&clickref=---DXTECH-&ued=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sky.com%2Fdeals%2Ffeatured&platform=pl" target="_blank" onclick="ExpressApp.GoogleAnalytics.TrackEvent('Affiliate widget', 'Get Sky TV + Netflix and broadband')"> <picture> <source srcset="https://cdn.images.express.co.uk/img/dynamic/affiliateswidgets/175x108/1675690438872.avif" type="image/avif"> <source srcset="https://cdn.images.express.co.uk/img/dynamic/affiliateswidgets/175x108/1675690438872.webp" type="image/webp"> <img src="https://cdn.images.express.co.uk/img/dynamic/affiliateswidgets/175x108/1675690438872.jpg" alt="Deal image" loading="lazy"> </picture> </a> <span class="partner-img"> <picture> <source srcset="https://cdn.images.express.co.uk/img/dynamic/af